name: Diversion - United 777-222ER [N795UA] Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Follow me on Flickr: https://www.flickr.com/photos/dude8472productions/

Today, December 23rd, this 777-200ER from United Airlines, flying LHR-SFO diverted to Calgary Airport at 1530 local time due to a medical emergency, leaving 90 minutes later at 1700. This video includes the taxi, ATC, and takeoff from 35L in the last bits of light. Enjoy!

Side note: Some of your comments have been flagged as spam for some reason and I haven't been able to reply to them, so my apologies.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
